The project name is : # SportiPal
_______________________________
  The brief conecpt is a game, |
that plays by self-movements.  |
We connect a camera, tracking  |
your movements. The hands that |
are now tracked are used to    |
touch colored circles to gain  |
points. The goal of the game   |
is to obtain the most points   |
possible, by maintaining a     |
regular activity, by moving to |
touch them.                    |
_______________________________|
